check = 1;
} else {
return false;
}
});

	<script>

	function listRemarketing() {
		let ProductResults = [];
		let productIds = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .product_id');

		for(let i = 0; i < productIds.length; i++){
			ProductResults.push({id:productIds[i].innerText})
		}
		dataLayer.push({
			'event_name': 'view_item_list',
			'value':'',
			'content_type': 'product_group',
			'items':ProductResults

		});
	}
	document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", listRemarketing);
</script>

	<script>

	function productImpressions() {

	let pagetype= document.getElementsByTagName('main')[0].dataset.pagetype;
	let parameter = document.getElementsByTagName('main')[0].dataset.parameter;
	let listname;

		if(pagetype === 'category'){
			listname='category list-'+ parameter;
		}
		else{
			let pathArray = window.location.pathname.split('/');
			let slug= pathArray[pathArray.length - 1 ];
			listname='collection list-' + slug;
		}


		let productImpressions = [];
		let productIds = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .product_id');
		let productName = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .name');
		let productPrice = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .price');
		let productBrand = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .brand');
		let productCategory = document.querySelector('.data_product_detail .category');
		let productPosition = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .position');
		for (let i = 0; i < productIds.length; i++) {
			productImpressions.push({
				id: productIds[i].innerText,
				name: productName[i].innerText.trim(),
				price: (parseFloat( productPrice[i].innerText)/1.24).toFixed(2),
				brand: productBrand[i].innerText.trim(),
				category: productCategory.innerText.trim(),
				position: productPosition[i].innerText.trim(),
				list: listname
			})

		}
		dataLayer.push({
			'ecommerce': {
				'currencyCode': 'EUR',
				'impressions': productImpressions
			}
		});
	};
	
	function productDetails() {
        let productEntryIds = document.querySelectorAll('.product[data-id]');
    	let productIds = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .product_id');
		let productName = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .name');
		let productPrice = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .price');
		let productBrand = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .brand');
		let productCategory = document.querySelector('.data_product_detail .category');
		let productPosition = document.querySelectorAll('.data_product_detail .position');
		 
		let products = {};

		for (let i = 0; i < productIds.length; i++) {
			products[productIds[i].innerText] =  {                 	
	            'productId': productEntryIds[i].getAttribute('data-id'),
	            'name': productName[i].innerText.trim(),
	            'id': productIds[i].innerText,
	            'price': productPrice[i].innerText.trim() ,
	            'brand': productBrand[i].innerText.trim(),
	            'category':productCategory.innerText.trim(),
	            'position': productPosition[i].innerText.trim()
	      }
		}
		window.page_details['products'] = products;
    };
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", productImpressions);
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", productDetails);
</script>

		'invalidGiftCardAmount' : 'Το ποσό της δωροκάρτας είναι μεγαλύτερο από την αξία του καλαθιού σου. Για να μπορέσεις να την εξαργυρώσεις θα πρέπει το καλάθι σου να είναι ίσης ή μεγαλύτερης αξίας από την αξία της δωροκάρτας.'
	};

	var absoluteURL = "https://www.kotsovolos.gr/";
	var absoluteBaseURL = "";

	//Summary: Returns the absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
	//Returns: The absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
	function getAbsoluteURL() {
		if (absoluteURL != "") {
			var currentURL = document.URL;
			var currentProtocol = "";

			if (currentURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				currentProtocol = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			var savedProtocol = "";
			if (absoluteURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				savedProtocol = absoluteURL.substring(0, absoluteURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			if (currentProtocol != savedProtocol) {
				absoluteURL = currentProtocol
						+ absoluteURL.substring(absoluteURL.indexOf("://"));
			}
		}

		return absoluteURL;
	}
	function getAbsoluteBaseURL() {
		if (absoluteBaseURL != "") {
			var currentURL = document.URL;
			var currentProtocol = "";

			if (currentURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				currentProtocol = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			var savedProtocol = "";
			if (absoluteBaseURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				savedProtocol = absoluteBaseURL.substring(0, absoluteURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			if (currentProtocol != savedProtocol) {
				absoluteBaseURL = currentProtocol
						+ absoluteBaseURL.substring(absoluteBaseURL
								.indexOf("://"));
			}
		}

		return absoluteBaseURL;
	}
</script>

    let isKotsOpen = 'true';
    let today = new Date();
    let diff = Math.abs(today.getTimezoneOffset() / 60);
    let hourInAthens = today.getUTCHours() + diff;
    let dayOfWeek = today.getDay();

    // If it's National Day or any other day in which we want to show only Offline
    //  if (dayOfWeek == 1) {
    //    isKotsOpen = "false";

    // else if {

        // //         // if it's before 11 or after 7, we're closed
        // if (hourInAthens < 11 || hourInAthens >= 20) {
        //     isKotsOpen = 'false';

    }
    // if it's Saturday
    else if (dayOfWeek == 6) {
        // if it's before 10 or after 6, we're closed
        if (hourInAthens < 9 || hourInAthens >= 20) {
            isKotsOpen = 'false';
        }
        // if it's Weekday
    } else {
        // if it's before 10 or after 8, we're closed

					<script>

$(document).ready(function() {
	cookieSetUp();
});

$(document).on("click", "#CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonLevelOptinAllowAll", function(){
    cookieSetUp();
});

$(document).on("click", "#CybotCookiebotDialogBodyLevelButtonLevelOptinAllowallSelection", function(){
    cookieSetUp();
});

function cookieSetUp(){
/* linkwise-footer-content */


	const url = window.location.href;
	const expiryDays = 30;

	let paidUrlType, lkws_138ID, affiliateCookie;
	let cookieConsent = $("#cookiebanner").length;
	let paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
	let referrer = document.referrer;

	console.log('version 1.4');

	if (url.indexOf('lkws_138') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('lkws_138') > 0) {
		if (url.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') < 0 && referrer.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') < 0){
			lkws_138ID = getParameterByName ('lkws_138', url);
			if (lkws_138ID == null) {
				lkws_138ID = getParameterByName ('lkws_138', referrer);
			}
			paidUrlType = lkws_138ID;
			sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
			paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');		
		}
		else if (url.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') > 0) {
			paidUrlType = "cookiePricePaidLastReferral";
			sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
			paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
		
		} 
		
	} else if (url.indexOf('fbclid') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('fbclid') > 0) {
		paidUrlType = "fbPaidLastReferral";
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');

	} else if (url.indexOf('gclid') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('gclid') > 0) {
		paidUrlType = "gPaidLastReferral";
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
		
	}  else if (url.indexOf('cmicc=skroutz') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('cmicc=skroutz') > 0) {
		paidUrlType = "skroutzPaidLastReferral";
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
		
	}   else if (url.indexOf('bpgid:') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('bpgid:') > 0) {
		paidUrlType = "bestPricePaidLastReferral";
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
		
	} else if (url.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') > 0 || referrer.indexOf('adhocPriceActive=true') > 0) {
		paidUrlType = "cookiePricePaidLastReferral";
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		paidSession = sessionStorage.getItem('paidSession');
		
	} 
	

	if (paidUrlType !== undefined && paidSession !== undefined) {
		sessionStorage.removeItem('paidSession');
		sessionStorage.setItem('paidSession', paidUrlType);
		
	}	
		
	
	setTimeout(function() {
		if (paidSession !== null && getCookie("CookieConsent")!== '' && getCookie("CookieConsent")!== null) {
			switch (paidUrlType) {
				case lkws_138ID:
					if (lkws_138ID !== undefined) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", lkws_138ID, expiryDays);	
					}else {
						setCookie("lkws_138", paidSession, expiryDays);	
					}						
					break;
				case "fbPaidLastReferral":
					affiliateCookie = getCookie("lkws_138");
					if (affiliateCookie !== '' && affiliateCookie !== null) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", "fbPaidLastReferral");					
					}
					break;
				case "gPaidLastReferral":
					affiliateCookie = getCookie("lkws_138");
					if (affiliateCookie !== '' && affiliateCookie !== null) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", "gPaidLastReferral");					
					}
					break;
				case "skroutzPaidLastReferral":
					affiliateCookie = getCookie("lkws_138");
					if (affiliateCookie !== '' && affiliateCookie !== null) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", "skroutzPaidLastReferral");					
					}
					break;
				case "bestPricePaidLastReferral":
					affiliateCookie = getCookie("lkws_138");
					if (affiliateCookie !== '' && affiliateCookie !== null) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", "bestPricePaidLastReferral");					
					}
					break;
				case "cookiePricePaidLastReferral":
					affiliateCookie = getCookie("lkws_138");
					if (affiliateCookie !== '' && affiliateCookie !== null) {
						setCookie("lkws_138", "cookiePricePaidLastReferral");					
					}
			}			
		}
	}, 2000);	
}
	function setCookie(cname, cvalue, exdays) {
		var d = new Date();
		d.setTime(d.getTime() + (exdays * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
		var expires = "expires=" + d.toGMTString();
		document.cookie = cname + "=" + cvalue + ";" + expires + ";path=/";
	}
	function getCookie(cname) {
		var name = cname + "=";
		var decodedCookie = decodeURIComponent(document.cookie);
		var ca = decodedCookie.split(';');
		for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
			var c = ca[i];
			while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') {
				c = c.substring(1);
			}
			if (c.indexOf(name) == 0) {
				return c.substring(name.length, c.length);
			}
		}
		return "";
	}
	function getParameterByName(name, url) {
		name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, '\\$&');
		var regex = new RegExp('[?&]' + name + '(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)'),
			results = regex.exec(url);
		if (!results) return null;
		if (!results[2]) return '';
		return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, ' '));
	}
</script>

	//Summary: Returns the absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
	//Returns: The absolute URL to use for prefixing any Ajax URL call.
	function getAbsoluteURL() {
		if (absoluteURL != "") {
			var currentURL = document.URL;
			var currentProtocol = "";

			if (currentURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				currentProtocol = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			var savedProtocol = "";
			if (absoluteURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				savedProtocol = absoluteURL.substring(0, absoluteURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			if (currentProtocol != savedProtocol) {
				absoluteURL = currentProtocol
						+ absoluteURL.substring(absoluteURL.indexOf("://"));
			}
		}

		return absoluteURL;
	}
	function getAbsoluteBaseURL() {
		if (absoluteBaseURL != "") {
			var currentURL = document.URL;
			var currentProtocol = "";

			if (currentURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				currentProtocol = currentURL.substring(0, currentURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			var savedProtocol = "";
			if (absoluteBaseURL.indexOf("://") != -1) {
				savedProtocol = absoluteBaseURL.substring(0, absoluteURL
						.indexOf("://"));
			}

			if (currentProtocol != savedProtocol) {
				absoluteBaseURL = currentProtocol
						+ absoluteBaseURL.substring(absoluteBaseURL
								.indexOf("://"));
			}
		}

		return absoluteBaseURL;
	}
</script>
